title: destinator 7 pc maps Denmark Norway Sweden Finland
description:
destinator 7 pc maps (Denmark, Norway, Sweden, Finland)

For more countries, please tell me and I will add them!


How to use:

1) Double-click the icon "My Computer" , then your local hard disk icon and then the folder "Program Files".

2) Find the folder where "Destinator 7" is installed(if not there, check elsewhere) and then add the downloaded folder with the maps.

Execute "Destinator 7" and select the desired map!
